title: Missouri coronavirus cases rise as stay-at-home order nears
description: JEFFERSON CITY, Mo. (AP) — Missouri reported 10 more deaths from COVID-19 Sunday, even while a national database was reporting a higher number in the state.
content:
JEFFERSON CITY, Mo. (AP) Missouri reported 10 more deaths from COVID-19 Sunday, even while a national database was reporting a higher number in the state.
